org.apache.streams.core

Interface StreamsProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable, StreamsOperation
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    StreamsPersistReader

    public interface StreamsProvider
extends StreamsOperation
    A StreamsProvider represents the entry point into the Streams pipeline. Providers are responsible for inserting data into the pipeline in discrete result sets.
